1. Install conda on your machine
2. Create a conda environment using following command:
    conda create -n circusaibackendv2 python=3.9.19
                        or
    conda create -n circusaibackendv2 python=3.9
3. Activate conda environment using following command:
    conda activate circusaibackend
4. 'cd' inside 'backend' folder
5. Run:
    pip install -r requirements.txt
6. To run the backend server 'cd' inside 'backend/django_app/' and run the following:
    python manage.py runserver